headline.main: A-Rod Cousin to Drop Not-Guilty Plea in Baseball Doping Scandal
headline.print_headline: A-Rod Cousin to Drop Not-Guilty Plea in Baseball Doping Scandal

docs.snippet: A cousin of Alex Rodriguez who linked the New York Yankees slugger to baseball's doping scandal plans to change his plea of not guilty on charges of distributing performance-enhancing drugs, records filed on Friday in Miami federal court showed....
